Product Application 


The relationship is not maintain using hibernate. 
- One to many 
- many to many 
- 


Product table 
 - proID - primaykey
 - name
 - description
 - Price
 - Status 
 - Date of launch 
 
Product Category 
 - catId - primaykey
 - Name 
 - Description

ProCat
 - proCatId - primaykey
 - proId - foriegnkey   p1  p2  p1    
 - catId - foriegnkey   c1  c2  c3

